[[File:Sweden_coat.png|25x25px|link=]]<span style="background-color: #e4edf5; border-radius: 2px">''Baroness''</span>[[File:Sweden_coat.png|25x25px|link=]] '''Ella Nilsson''' (b. March 24, 1901 — d. ???) is a Swedish baroness, born to [[Lars Nilsson]] and Molly Nilsson, the legal heir to a fifth of her father's estate and the secondary successor of the Nilsson branch. At birth she was identified as the Baroness of Kungelv.<br>
